                <head>21. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>On August 8, the Third Emergency Special Session of the <gloss target="#t_UN1"
                        >U.N</gloss>. General Assembly convened to discuss the situation in the
                    Middle East. The Special Session lasted through August 21. Documentation on the
                    Special Session is scheduled for publication in volume XI.</p>
            </div>
